title: Bruce Springsteen Tunnel of love DVD
description:
Video/DVD of the Tunnel of love express tour

Idraetspark In Copenhagen Denmark 25th july 1988:
Spare Parts, War, Born In The USA,Chimes Of Freedom,Paradise By The "C", Who Do You Love/ She's The One, You Can Look, I'm A Coward.
St.Jacobs Stadion in Basel Switserland 14th july 1988:
Follow That Dream, Bobby Jean, Caddilac Ranch, Tenth Avenue Freeze Out, Sweet Soul Music, Raise Your Hand, Twist And Shout.
Shoreline Amphitheater in Mountainview California 2nd May 1988:
Be True.
Weissensee Cycling Track in East Berlin East Germany 19th july 1988:
Can't Help Falling In Love,.
On The Streets Of Copenhagen Denmark 23rd july 1988:
I'm On Fire, The River, Dancing In The Dark
